\sum_{m=2}^\infty(-1)^{m-1}\frac{m-1}{(2m)!}=-\sum_{m=2}^\infty(-1)^{m}\frac{m}{(2m)!}+\sum_{m=2}^\infty(-1)^{m} \frac{1}{(2m)!}
=-\sum_{m=2}^\infty(-1)^{m}\frac{1}{2(2m-1)!}+\sum_{m=0}^\infty(-1)^{m} \frac{1}{(2m)!}-1+\frac{1}{2!}
\frac{m}{(2m)!}=\frac{m}{(2m)(2m-1)!}=\frac{1}{(2)(2m-1)!}
